    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This issue is only related to incompatibility between Project SDK, Spring Boot and Lombok versions. These two pairs of old and new versions work well together. Note to check the &quot;Project Structure&quot; to make sure the correct SDK is set for the project. Check out the screenshot below each sample for more clarity.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Old versions\n<ul>\n<li>JDK 1.8</li>\n<li>Spring Boot 2.7.2</li>\n<li>Lombok 1.18.20</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/dIHz0.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/dIHz0.png\" alt=\"compatible old versions\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>New versions\n<ul>\n<li>JDK 21</li>\n<li>Spring Boot 3.2.4</li>\n<li>Lombok 1.18.30\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/FhM1y.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/FhM1y.png\" alt=\"compatible new versions\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3177801,
      "reputation" : 101,
      "user_id" : 2685233,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/54f056c84e824c5a6c1c2afebb966a2e?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "naveenz",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2685233/naveenz"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1716995158,
    "creation_date" : 1716995158,
    "answer_id" : 78550455,
    "question_id" : 77297895,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Got this error with lombok version 1.18.20. mvn clean package was failed. Updating with 1.18.22 didn't work but 1.18.30 worked.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 25030468,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 18888289,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GgN0-npU_635nIwmRpoo7Y6qZk1TXpC-5pLONl7kg=k-s256",
      "display_name" : "Nishant Bodade",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/18888289/nishant-bodade"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1718528890,
    "last_edit_date" : 1718528890,
    "creation_date" : 1718528123,
    "answer_id" : 78628690,
    "question_id" : 77297895,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The error message is occurring due to the use of older versions of Spring Boot, Lombok, and JDK. After updating to the latest versions, you should be able to build successfully.</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;parent&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;3.3.0&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;relativePath/&gt; &lt;!-- lookup parent from repository --&gt;\n &lt;/parent&gt;\n\n &lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;java.version&gt;21&lt;/java.version&gt;\n &lt;/properties&gt;\n\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n        &lt;version&gt;1.18.32&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 29132750,
      "reputation" : 61,
      "user_id" : 22317602,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTtdEy6eYoUrzHLmf1jnbn13mPBndSF3BcFQ3s5h6nJU5ZQ=k-s256",
      "display_name" : "JinghuaOriental",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/22317602/jinghuaoriental"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 5,
    "last_activity_date" : 1727334432,
    "creation_date" : 1727334432,
    "answer_id" : 79025927,
    "question_id" : 77297895,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can try to modify lombok's version, update (exactly).</p>\n<p>Usually the newest version will be OK. As follows.</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.18.34&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 10919070,
      "reputation" : 393,
      "user_id" : 8025999,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-0TxyDM2U36s/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAEQw/AXuX115WCtY/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "m Piroli",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/8025999/m-piroli"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1735947653,
    "creation_date" : 1735947653,
    "answer_id" : 79327938,
    "question_id" : 77297895,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>pls check if you have correct java version into runner <a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LhMjPEUd.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LhMjPEUd.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 15249626,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 11003452,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-_idPHYYzPLI/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/ACevoQN5Mt62iNgcHLvhWYRVT7dbGsOeSA/mo/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "Miguel Ruiz Velasco",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/11003452/miguel-ruiz-velasco"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1758760634,
    "creation_date" : 1758760634,
    "answer_id" : 79774279,
    "question_id" : 77297895,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As other answers stated: This error is some incompatibility between the JDK, Lombok and (maybe) Springboot.</p>\n<p>But there is a simpler fix: simply let Springboot manage the Lombok version via it's managed dependencies.</p>\n<p>You only have to import the <strong><code>spring-boot-starter-parent</code></strong> as your parent project. You can also import the <code>spring-boot-starter-dependencies</code> BOM in <code>&lt;dependency-management&gt;</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;project xmlns=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0&quot; xmlns:xsi=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot; xsi:schemaLocation=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 https://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;modelVersion&gt;4.0.0&lt;/modelVersion&gt;\n...\n  &lt;parent&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;3.5.3&lt;/version&gt;\n  &lt;/parent&gt;\n  \n  &lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;java.jdk.version&gt;17&lt;/java.jdk.version&gt;\n    &lt;maven.compiler.target&gt;17&lt;/maven.compiler.target&gt;\n    &lt;maven.compiler.source&gt;17&lt;/maven.compiler.source&gt;\n    &lt;swagger-version&gt;3.0.0&lt;/swagger-version&gt;\n  &lt;/properties&gt;\n  \n  &lt;dependencies&gt;\n...\n    &lt;dependency&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;!--        Let spring boot BOM manage Lombok's version --&gt;\n    &lt;/dependency&gt;\n...\n  &lt;/dependencies&gt;\n\n\n&lt;/project&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
